    The hotel was very good and we had no complaints.

    The hotel was very good and we had no complaints. The Booking.com service I used to reserve two rooms was absolutely the worst customer experience ever. Fortunately the hotel reservation agent was able to sort out the issues. Although we paid in good faith months ago, this booking service only released the funds for one room. Consequently, we were waiting for an hour at the front desk to check in and missed part of the event we came to Hartford to see. With much help and kindness from the hotel reception agent and the hotel manager, we were able to secure both rooms. We cannot thank them enough for going out of their way to help us. The Booking.com agent was the worst and failed to help both the hotel and us resolve the booking error made by their service.
    Guest review by
    Betty
    United States

    Beautiful city if you stay at the right place.

    Beautiful city if you stay at the right place. There's a lot to explore. The food was delicious and I was unaware of this beforehand because it can actually be really hard to find the good places when trying to look them up. It's almost better to drive around until you see something you might want to check out. For reference I ate at the Max Downtown and Trumbull Kitchen. Also there are parking garages literally everywhere. Just be aware of their closing times.
    Guest review by

Overall, my stay was enjoyable.

How does it work?

  • 1

    It starts with a booking

    It starts with a booking

    The only way to leave a review is to first make a booking. That's how we know our reviews come from real guests who have stayed at the property.

  • 2

    Followed by a trip

    Followed by a trip

    When guests stay at the property, they check out how quiet the room is, how friendly the staff is, and more.

  • 3

    And finally, a review

    And finally, a review

    After their trip, guests tell us about their stay. We check for naughty words and verify the authenticity of all guest reviews before adding them to our site.

If you booked through us and want to leave a review, please sign in first.
